reviewText: I bought this because i wanna watch him eat those  Fokken Pancakes
I really enjoyed Marky Mark workout video because he is in great shape, he is so cute, and it shows how to eat right.
It's truly an inspiring video. Watch Marky stretch and exercise from the comfort of your couch. You may not loose much weight, but you are certain to enjoy every minute of this video.

Dear people,
At first, I bought this tape because I'm totally obssessed with Marky Mark a.k.a. Mark Wahlberg. It is a really cool workout tape. I lost weight and my body is more toned than ever. I followed his nutrition and workout advices and it works! And I use it all the time for my workout! I'd give to this tape 10 on 5 if I could. MARKY MARK ROCKS!

Ok, let me first say that the reason that I bought this movie at first was because I think that Mark Wahlberg is really hot and I love him, but when one day I was just watching this, I got really into it, and its great, now I use it all the time for my work out!! Its great, you get a work out- and you have one of the hottest guys on earth showing you how!!  ps- how can you NOT believe this works when you check out his body??
